[Student "S"]
{Once more, NORTH has the same hand as Deals 1 and 2.

This time SOUTH has a very poor hand without any chance of making game. However, he should bid 
4\S anyway.

It is very likely that the opponents can make 4\H if West gets the 
opportunity to get into the bidding. Hopefully the 4\S bid will shut him out, and 4\S probably 
won't go down more than a couple of tricks.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
[Board "3"]
[Dealer "E"]
[Vulnerable "EW"]
[Deal "E:43.85.KQJ9862.97 T982.JT43.AT.KJ2 KQ76.A62.53.AQ83 AJ5.KQ97.74.T654"]
[Declarer "E"]
[Contract "3D"]
